# Approach
Store all the edges in hash map.

addEdge - add one more node to edge.
shortestPath - implement optimal path finding using Heap. On each step go to next node with min total path. For this node add all reachable nodes from this node to the MinHeap. Priority will be cost to get to particular node.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
addEdge O(1)
shortestPath O(K*Nlog(N))

- Space complexity:
O(N)
