        heapq.heappush(pq, (0, node1))
        dist[node1] = 0

        while pq:
            cost, curr = heapq.heappop(pq)
            if curr == node2:
                return cost
            for neighbour, cost in self.graph[curr]:
                if dist[neighbour] > dist[curr] + cost:
                    dist[neighbour] = dist[curr] + cost
                    heapq.heappush(pq, (dist[neighbour], neighbour))
        return -1
```

