# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
The idea here is to iterate over the array and store the elements in a temp array until the temp array reaches the size limit. Once the limit is reached temp array is pushed into result array.

At the end of for loop , left over elements from temp array can be pushed ( if there is any )
